tests.context:
{
  "title": "Conversation Log",
  "value": "#me: Freshman & First-Time
#bot: To apply as first time freshmen, you must meet the following requirements:
✔️ Be high school graduate or equivalent
✔️ Complete the fifteen-unit comprehensive A-G course pattern of college preparatory study with grades of 'C' or better.
✔️ Meet the eligibility index (local area students held to minimum eligibility index. Non-local students are held to higher index).
Please refer to our website https://www.kommunicate.io/ for further information regarding First-year Students admissions."
}
